Subject: drm/v3d: Convert to platform remove callback returning void
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: b957812839f87d83cf8189818da73d84df6f263f
